                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/liudaxian/">青年哪吒</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar20 rating" title="较差"></span>
                    <span>2013-12-12</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">盛名之下，其实难副</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="408386074">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-408386074" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-408386074" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="408386074">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/chengximin/">橙子</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2012-12-07</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">可能还是周锡瑞说的对，晚清的满汉问题，其实并不是族群问题，而是反特权的问题，这就能解释为何在辛亥革命后，反满口号迅速的销声匿迹了。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="475236059">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-475236059" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-475236059" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="475236059">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2097800/">ici</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-08-28</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">师姐翻译，质量保证。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="353080784">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-353080784" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-353080784" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="353080784">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xinchai1998/">信差</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2011-04-05</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">关于族群关系本身的叙述似乎不如清末民初政局分析的篇章分量多，让人质疑满汉关系在此一时期的政治生活中是否真的是一个极其重要关节点。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="537363245">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-537363245" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-537363245" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="537363245">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/17884700/">Ricardo</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-05-28</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">主要涉及耳熟能详的近代史历程中,满与汉两个族群在政治权力上的角逐,这中间又夹杂着革命过程中激化的对于旗人的暴行,令其不容易看清继而又影响到前者对于自己自身身份的重新认同.青山依旧在,一时之成败,真是难说的紧.</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

